Blindness Elimination for just

00:13:29.170 --> 00:13:30.120
a small place.

00:13:30.120 --> 00:13:34.170
They need to verify
for the entire country.

00:13:34.170 --> 00:13:38.140
And then we have cross-border
transmission issues.

00:13:38.140 --> 00:13:40.190
And for some countries,
mapping agencies

00:13:40.190 --> 00:13:42.440
have not updated their maps.

00:13:42.440 --> 00:13:44.140
And we need this type of maps.

00:13:46.750 --> 00:13:49.100
And sometimes they're
not available.

00:13:49.100 --> 00:13:52.240
Where are the communities?

