Sometimes it's a
jungle, like the Amazon.

00:13:55.090 --> 00:13:57.430
Where are the communities
that are affected.

00:13:57.430 --> 00:14:00.020
Mapping Onchocerciasis
is warranted

00:14:00.020 --> 00:14:01.860
when an area is inhabited.

00:14:01.860 --> 00:14:04.370
Because the human
disease-- we need

00:14:04.370 --> 00:14:05.980
to find-- if there are humans.

00:14:05.980 --> 00:14:07.870
That's when we go
to the mapping.

00:14:07.870 --> 00:14:11.330
But if you don't
have the technology,

00:14:11.330 --> 00:14:13.290
you will go and find nobody.

00:14:13.290 --> 00:14:15.130
And you will have been
wasting resources.

00:14:15.130 --> 00:14:16.730
But if you have
technology and you

00:14:16.730 --> 00:14:19.170
know-- you can tell that
there are communities,

00:14:19.170 --> 00:14:21.190
then you can go where
you-- where you already

00:14:21.190 --> 00:14:24.550
